===Noun===
'''conterminous'''
# Sharing a single external border, as the forty-eight ''conterminous'' United States. Similar to the City and County of San Francisco. Their borders are one and the same. Conterminous regions may have different names, hence "Brooklyn" and "Kings County" in New York.
#:''The forty-eight '''conterminous''' states do not include Alaska or Hawaii.''

